𝑶𝒉 𝒂𝒏𝒐, 𝒃𝒂𝒃𝒂𝒅 𝒏𝒂 𝒃𝒂𝒃𝒂𝒅 𝒏𝒂 𝒂𝒌𝒐 𝒅𝒊𝒕𝒐 𝒐𝒉 💦 𝒃𝒂𝒌𝒂 𝒑𝒘𝒆𝒅𝒆 𝒎𝒐 𝒏𝒂𝒎𝒂𝒏𝒈 🫣 𝒉𝒖𝒊 𝒏𝒐 𝒅𝒂𝒘 𝒂𝒏𝒐𝒏𝒈 𝒑𝒘𝒆𝒅𝒆 𝒎𝒐 𝒏𝒂𝒎𝒂𝒏𝒈 🥵 𝒂𝒏𝒐 𝒉𝒎𝒎 𝒕𝒂𝒎𝒂 𝒏𝒂 𝒏𝒈𝒂 🥴

✨ CALL FOR PARTICIPANTS ✨

Greetings of Fortitude, Excellence, and Uprightness! 🔰
We are 4th-year Far Eastern University students from the Department of Psychology and we are inviting you to participate in our qualitative research study titled “The Lived Experiences of Young Adult Filipino Women Who Use Birth Control Pills for Contraception”.
Our study aims to gain insight about the reproductive health experiences of young adult Filipino women who use pills for contraceptive purposes.

𝗤𝘂𝗮𝗹𝗶𝗳𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀:
🎀 Must be 18 to 30 years old
🎀 Biological Female
🎀 Used or is using hormonal contraceptive pills for 3-4 months or more
🎀 Does not use any other forms of hormonal contraceptive methods (implants, patches, injections and IUDs)
🎀 Does not use hormonal pills for any other purposes aside from contraception (Menstrual regulation or Gender-affirming treatment)
🎀 Resides in Metro Manila

The study will be a face-to-face interview setup. The details of the interview may be discussed further.

If you are interested to participate, please fill out the pre-registration form below:
https://forms.gle/fK92DxBiNrCeYAp38

For inquiries, please contact any of the following researchers below:
👤 Nicole Anne B. Delos Santos
Contact No.: 0915-898-9984
Email:2022064961@feu.edu.ph
👤 Mikaela Sophia F. Galias
Contact No.: 0995-963-9980
Email: 2021034831@feu.edu.ph

Thank you!

🎀 Must be 18 to 30 years old
🎀 Biological Female
🎀 Used or is using hormonal contraceptive pills for 3-4 months or more
🎀 Does not use any other forms of hormonal contraceptive methods (implants, patches, injections and IUDs)
🎀 Does not use hormonal pills for any other purposes aside from contraception (Menstrual regulation or Gender-affirming treatment)
🎀 Resides in Metro Manila

The study will be a face-to-face interview setup. The details of the interview may be discussed further.

If you are interested to participate, please fill out the pre-registration form below:
https://forms.gle/fK92DxBiNrCeYAp38

For inquiries, please contact any of the following researchers below:

👤 Mikaela Sophia F. Galias
Contact No.: 0995-963-9980
Email: 2021034831@feu.edu.ph

Thank you!
